subject: Tennis
Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
lead_paragraph: The top-ranked Djokovic defeated Richard Gasquet, 7-6 (2), 6-4, 6-4, to advance to his fourth Wimbledon final. He will face Federer, who beat Andy Murray, 7-5, 7-5, 6-4.
